WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.730
Your competitor isn't better than you. They're just more available.

00:00:04.730 --> 00:00:09.200
Mental availability is who comes to mind first, not who's best.

00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:16.200
Memory is real estate. Whoever occupies the space first wins, before quality is ever compared.

00:00:16.200 --> 00:00:21.700
Think about the last time you needed a service and only one name came to mind.

00:00:21.700 --> 00:00:28.900
That wasn't loyalty. That was mental availability. Build it before you ever have to compete on price.

00:00:28.900 --> 00:00:33.170
Being good isn't a strategy. Being remembered is.

00:00:33.170 --> 00:00:36.670
Perception and attention intelligence.

00:00:36.670 --> 00:00:43.770
If you want to know whether you're the name that comes to mind, the audit is free. No pitch. Just arstrategies.com.
